      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a functional and affordable car. It's a great opportunity to own a solid vehicle at a fantastic price!",
