      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Draped in a finish of deep midnight sapphire that seems to swallow the moonlight, this isn't just a vehicle\u2014it\u2019s a masterpiece in motion. Slide into the cockpit and you are instantly enveloped by the rich, intoxicating aroma of hand-stitched leather and the quiet promise of the open road. Every line of its sleek silhouette whispers a story of elegance and untamed power, a timeless icon that has been cherished like a family secret. When the engine awakens, it doesn't just start; it exhales a soulful, rhythmic purr that resonates in your chest. This is more than a purchase; it is an invitation to inhabit a legacy of grace and breathtaking performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
